Event Addis
Event Addis is a web application designed to simplify event management by allowing users to post and discover events happening in Addis Ababa, Ethiopia.


Features
Event Creation: Organizers can easily create and manage events by providing details such as title, date, location, description, and more.
Event Discovery: Users can browse and search for events based on different criteria like date, location, category, etc.
Registration and Ticketing: Seamless registration and ticketing system for users to sign up for events and purchase tickets if applicable.
User Authentication: Secure user authentication system with login and logout functionalities.
Responsive Design: The application is built with a responsive design to ensure compatibility across various devices and screen sizes.
Technologies Used
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap
Backend: Python, Flask
Database: SQLite
APIs: Twilio (for SMS notifications), Google Maps (for location services)
